@node "FAQSPS2M" "FAQ: What is a PS2M Hardware?"
@toc "FAQS"

 @{MS "What is a PS2M Hardware?"}

PS2M is a PC Mouse interface. It allows to connect any modern PS2 Mouse to Amiga. It even supports
the MouseWheel and additional buttons.@{par}

For more information take a look into the archive: "Aminet/hard/hack/ps2m.lha"@{par}

@endnode

